Hello <%= @friendship.receiver.nickname %>,

We are pleased to inform you that you have received a new friend request on <%= ApplicationMailer::APP_NAME %>

<b>Details of the Friend Request:</b>

Sender's Nickname: <%= @friendship.sender.nickname %>

Date Submitted: <%= @friendship.created_at.strftime('%d.%m.%Y at %H:%M') %>

To view and respond to this friend request, please click on the link below:
<%= link_to "My Friend page", @url %>

You can accept or decline the friend request by clicking the appropriate button.

<%= link_to "Accept", @accept_url %> <%= link_to "Decline", @decline_url %>

Thank you for using <%= ApplicationMailer::APP_NAME %>.

